    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Standard comprising descriptions and names of 267 color blocks devised by the Inter-Society Color Council (ISCC) and the the United States Department of Commerce's National Bureau of Standards (NBS) (now called the National Institute of Standards and Technology).</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
